  "body_html": "<p align=\"left\" style=\"font-size: medium; font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><b>2025년 11월 1일(토) 비발디파크 (구)골프연습장 에서 개최된</b></span></div><p align=\"left\" style=\"font-size: medium; font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">&#65279;<b>&#8203;2025 하반기 FCI 인터내셔널 어질리티 경기대회 결과표입니다.</b></span>&nbsp;</div><p align=\"left\" style=\"font-size: medium; font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;;\">&nbsp;</div><p align=\"left\" style=\"font-size: medium; font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.6667px;\"><b>※ 최종 마이크로칩이 등록이 안된 견들은 표기되어 있으며 경기대회는 번외처리 됩니다.</b></span></div><p align=\"left\" style=\"font-size: medium; font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.6667px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><b>&nbsp;(공식대회 기록 및 상력 인정 불가: FCI 규정 의거 혈통서상 마이크로칩 미등록 시 출진 자체 불가)</b></span></div><p align=\"left\" style=\"font-size: medium; font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.6667px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><b><br></b></span></div><p align=\"left\" style=\"font-size: medium; font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.6667px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><b><img src=\"https://www.thekkf.or.kr/kkf_file/item/1763540771_fl4fenrJLOEMkdCbnwo5wLMa5unwmP.jpg\" title=\"%255B%25B0%25E1%25B0%25FA%25B1%25E2%25BE%25C8%255D2025%2B%25C7%25CF%25B9%25DD%25B1%25E2%2BFCI%2B%25C0%25CE%25C5%25CD%25B3%25BB%25BC%25C5%25B3%25CE%2B%25BE%25EE%25C1%25FA%25B8%25AE%25C6%25BC%2B%25B0%25E6%25B1%25E2%25B4%25EB%25C8%25B8002.jpg\"><br style=\"clear:both;\"><img src=\"https://www.thekkf.or.kr/kkf_file/item/1763540777_ZmRAoALik7zqaAnoiNS8Io6KrlodWW.jpg\" title=\"%255B%25B0%25E1%25B0%25FA%25B1%25E2%25BE%25C8%255D2025%2B%25C7%25CF%25B9%25DD%25B1%25E2%2BFCI%2B%25C0%25CE%25C5%25CD%25B3%25BB%25BC%25C5%25B3%25CE%2B%25BE%25EE%25C1%25FA%25B8%25AE%25C6%25BC%2B%25B0%25E6%25B1%25E2%25B4%25EB%25C8%25B8003.jpg\"><br style=\"clear:both;\"><img src=\"https: